{"tid":1816911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉］國際版五大訴求","createTime":"2020-01-08T15:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T06:21:22.000Z","uid":322454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc637501b1c7339d80f336399bf84a102daa7b8","tid":1816911,"uid":322454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"我地個5大訴求係比ccp睇的，ccp唔會理<br />\nSoloman 都話我地唔夠清晰目標<br />\n<br />\n不如做過國際版的訴求<br />\n不過要注意，人地唔會無限幫我地<br />\n內容要合乎人地的利益，唔可以要人蝕錢幫<br />\n<br />\n希望可以引更多人比建議<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n1. 希望各國能減少依賴中共及其同盟（違反人權的組織）之服務（eg 生產鏈改地點，華為5g之類）<br />\n<br />\n2. 加強打擊中共（違反人權組織）之滲透，調查被收買之人員<br />\n<br />\n3. 各國加強各政府機關互相制衡之能力（特別是武裝力量，冇制衡所有野都可能腐敗，香港係比較發達城市都9成黑警）<br />\n<br />\n4. 減少對資本的貪婪，唔好因為錢而放棄自己的價值觀，政府立國的根本信念<br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n<br />\n比你地念下"},{"pid":"77b3418402a8eba84aaf45b6b9ee7dbf2f40303a","tid":1816911,"uid":59297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5b01b6ac18f669552913812cd43894272b51fde","tid":1816911,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">將伊戰spin返返嚟香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8553a2c43c42d081359247ecf23f87ca48a845e9","tid":1816911,"uid":322454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n我係p"},{"pid":"e1c3e5155ebb38a8b600911d68b002d9f4a09fd0","tid":1816911,"uid":322454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n我係p<br />\n如果認同幫下手"},{"pid":"84702e5fc10b98ff7300d68312c39adf771edbe8","tid":1816911,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f7cb56e08495ed8dd133e03711750d9706467de","tid":1